channel.title: Some SSBB Models
channel.description:
Here's a download for Super Smash Brother's Brawl characters. I'm pretty sure most of you will love to have some of these. Some have textures some don't. The textures are included just not added onto models. 80% credits to Nintendo. 13% credits to Gazamaniac for ripping them. 7% to me for zipping, making Metaseq compatible and adding on here. Some of the characters it includes are: Ike [URL=http://img444.imageshack.us/i/ike.jpg/][IMG]http://img444.imageshack.us/img444/6595/ike.jpg[/img][/URL] Isaac Kat and Anna Link Lyn Marth Olimar Pikmin Poltergust 3000 Ridley Snake [URL=http://img215.imageshack.us/i/snakewg.jpg/][IMG]http://img215.imageshack.us/img215/8528/snakewg.jpg[/img][/URL] Tabuu Tabuu (wings) Zelda [URL=http://img696.imageshack.us/i/zeldal.jpg/][IMG]http://img696.imageshack.us/img696/7893/zeldal.jpg[/img][/URL] Zero-Suit Samus
You can change the model limits on any client here. http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,426139.0.html
Will post download links as I upload. http://uppit.com/v/ZXOGEK88 http://www.megaupload.com/?d=1MWBPYPL http://www.mediafire.com/?djy1ldy2gml
